
[1]uprightly

   UPRIGHTLY, adv.

   1. In a direction perpendicular to the plane of the horizon; in an
   erect position.

   2. Honestly; with strict observance of rectitude; as, to live
   uprightly.

   He that walketh uprightly, walketh surely. Prov. 10.
